{
  "id": "adv_main_01_07_10",
  "title": "星見編2章10話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（雫達の向かった方向は海岸だった）\n（二人はそこに並んで座っていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Shizuku and Chisa head towards the seafront.）\nThe two of them sit down there together.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.133333333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2633.333333333336,
          "startTime": 6.76666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたの、雫ちゃん\n……いきなりでビックリしちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s the matter‚ Shizuku-chan?\nYou gave me a surprise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……自分でも、ビックリしてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I surprised myself as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだったんだね……\nでも……正直ホッとしてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see…\nBut… to be honest‚ I’m relieved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.62578242619832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "うまくいかないなぁ、なんでかなぁ……って\n少し落ち込んでたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was feeling a bit down…….\n‘cause I felt like things weren’t going well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.448386611938474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……千紗……ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa…chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.68171994527181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、凄いよね\nさくらちゃんも、遙子さんも、怜ちゃんも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re amazing‚ aren’t they?\nSakura-chan‚ Haruko-san‚ and Rei-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.993397925694776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたら、なれるのかな……あんな風に\n全然わかんないよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder how I can become like that.\nI’ve got no clue…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.22673125902812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、千紗……ちゃん\nこっち",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Chisa-chan…\nLook.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.94524487495423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "え？ …………ぷっ！ あははっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Pfft… hahah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.34524487495423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "やだ、雫ちゃん！ な、何その顔……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously‚ Shizuku-chan! What’s with that face?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.53080033302308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "笑顔、うまく作れないから……\nこうして指で、変顔作ってみた……どやー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t make a proper smile‚…\nso I used my fingers to make a funny face. Wahoo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.49828321774801,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "あははっ！ そ、その顔はダメだよ！\nおかしいのに、かわいくて……あははっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahah! Th-that’s not fair!\nThat funny face is so adorable… Hahah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.63553823190574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（千紗がお腹を抱えて笑うのは初めて見たな）\n（ 雫も雫で、ああして人を笑わせられるのか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I’ve never seen Chisa laugh so hard before.）\n（I also didn’t know Shizuku could make people laugh like that.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.16887156523909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "自分では、笑顔、上手にできないけど\n千紗ちゃんを……笑顔に、できた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t make myself smile properly‚\nbut‚ Chisa-chan… I was able to make you smile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.50220489857242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "うん……そうだね\n雫ちゃんのおかげで、元気出たよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… you did.\nI feel much better‚ thanks to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.7688715652391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "私にとって、アイドルは……キラキラしてて\nファンに笑顔、届ける人達……だから、憧れた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For me‚ idols are sparkly people…\nwho make their fans smile… That’s why I admire them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.1355382319058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんも、いま、笑ってくれたから……\n私も少しは、アイドルになれた……かな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I was able to make you smile‚ Chisa-chan…\nI feel a little closer to being an idol… I think.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.90094500397431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.0522272411006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "落ち込んでる千紗ちゃん、見たくなくて……\nどうしたら、笑顔になって……くれるかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn’t wanna see you looking sad‚\nso I was wondering… what I could do to make you smile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.72612751156257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "それで……へ、変顔を？\nでも、どうしてそこまで……？？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that why you made that f-funny face?\nBut why go through all the trouble…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.22612751156257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hope-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 138.19279417822924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "……友達、だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because… you’re my friend.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.39279417822925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "…………っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.19279417822924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "アイドル向いてるって、言ってくれた……\n似た者同士だねって、言ってくれた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said I had potential as an idol…\nYou said the two of us were similar…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7927941782293,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "すごくうれしかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It made me really happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.05946084489597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "……雫ちゃん……\nそうだったんだね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan…\n…I had no idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.52612755924645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめん……わかりにくくて\n顔にも、口にも……出すの、下手だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry… for not making it clear.\nI’m not very good… at expressing myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.65946089257977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことない……そんなこと、ないよ\nすごく嬉しいよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not true… That’s not true at all.\nIt means so much to me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.29279422591307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "私だって、雫ちゃんの……友達だもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m your friend as well‚ Shizuku-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.05346695413368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_10-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "……ん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.4534670495011,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
